":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80670b8d60a416baa29478486fe93936e13fe282","tid":445051,"uid":24137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T23:58:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心疑惑唔使報年齡可以點配<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解唔得，睇完對方嘅介紹合適嘅咪入聊天室再互相了解，覺得年齡係個問題嘅可以係自我介紹寫埋等對方考慮或者放棄第3回合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc5dd728c99b97d35d7a26c6f7809f5672a74b4","tid":445051,"uid":24137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd71f90702259c2c78192a50834f8d9ac6c0ad6","tid":445051,"uid":25483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:02:35.000Z","msg":"我屌你個老母先啦 <br />\n點解個政治取向得咁撚少<br />\n 香港獨立去咗邊"},{"pid":"9373718dcf29d317014d2f2e4a422130087d834e","tid":445051,"uid":24137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T12:23:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b7e53d1f74ad6391e2564cadb3465530e47c917","tid":445051,"uid":24137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T16:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65658c3870fb15da8536e3c1cd09f17bdbf4ac5f","tid":445051,"uid":24137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T23:35:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f38112684d2951bdc3988b4033223424924f2ab","tid":445051,"uid":24137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T04:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d99f82a5bfdf6cf206cc23b60a9e5e00c9dbc3","tid":445051,"uid":154955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T07:35:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真心疑惑唔使報年齡可以點配<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解唔得，睇完對方嘅介紹合適嘅咪入聊天室再互相了解，覺得年齡係個問題嘅可以係自我介紹寫埋等對方考慮或者放棄第3回合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無話點解唔得 實得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好奇 + 建議姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇得星座既人點會唔在乎年齡 有既話都唔會係多數<br />\nset多個制俾人選年齡會好過你咁樣搞到又考慮又放棄"},{"pid":"1741857d940a3abf06cae8f6e8fbb18df13efb29","tid":445051,"uid":24137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T09:53:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真心疑惑唔使報年齡可以點配<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解唔得，睇完對方嘅介紹合適嘅咪入聊天室再互相了解，覺得年齡係個問題嘅可以係自我介紹寫埋等對方考慮或者放棄第3回合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無話點解唔得 實得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好奇 + 建議姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇得星座既人點會唔在乎年齡 有既話都唔會係多數<br />\nset多個制俾人選年齡會好過你咁樣搞到又考慮又放棄</blockquote><br />\n本身諗住有左個初步嘅配對先，等啲人自己係聊天室進一步認識。今次玩星座純粹係未試過想試下反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  btw多謝巴打建議 聖誕特別版會加入年齡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c6f6d63c74ab0e049adb2c553f042f5c543a20c","tid":445051,"uid":56763,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T16:49:25.000Z","msg":"上次派對獲得向各位巴絲支持 黎緊我地會再接再厲！！ <br />\n聖誕就黎到 大家有咩願望？ <br />\n想識到一班朋友 或者一個有緣人過聖誕？ <br />\n係到放低你的聖誕願望 <br />\n話唔定可以搵到同你實現願望的人 <br />\n到時會有小食同遊戲等緊你地！ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日子：26/11/2017 <br />\n地點：觀塘 <br />\n時間：3:00-7:00（暫定） <br />\n費用：$250(男) $100 (女) <br />\n<br />\n快啲填表啦~ <br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/VbimPjM60lxU4vTz2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FVbimPjM60lxU4vTz2&d=%2BWG9322KYsAL9bkPqjBoJ%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=ef8ff8d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/VbimPjM60lxU4vTz2</a>"}]}